---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Solutions — ruuley" canonical="/en/solutions/">
  <section class="hero container">
    <h1>Solutions</h1>
    <p>Industry-specific value realized by JSON-IR and Validation Gate</p>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Government & Public Sector</h3>
        <p><strong>Making Laws Computable and Public Infrastructure</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Structuring legal provisions through JSON-IR conversion</li>
          <li>Quality assurance through Validation Gate</li>
          <li>Management of entire legal systems via integrated bundles</li>
          <li>Tracking revision history through traceability</li>
          <li>Utilization as public APIs (open data)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Enterprise Compliance</h3>
        <p><strong>From Internal Regulations to Executable Rules</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>JSON-IR conversion of internal regulations and policies</li>
          <li>Automatic detection of violations through strict operations</li>
          <li>Integration and consistency checks of multiple regulations</li>
          <li>Backend code generation</li>
          <li>Automation of continuous regulation maintenance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Legal Publishing & Information Platforms</h3>
        <p><strong>Integrated Editing, Verification, and Distribution</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Efficient editing with advanced editors</li>
          <li>Automatic quality checks on save</li>
          <li>Natural language text management</li>
          <li>Visualization of editing processes</li>
          <li>Automatic conversion to multiple formats</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Law Firms & Consulting</h3>
        <p><strong>Knowledge Management and Reuse</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>JSON-IR library of case law and contract clauses</li>
          <li>Cross-cutting search via Integration Bundler</li>
          <li>Automatic discovery of similar clauses and pattern extraction</li>
          <li>Contract drafting support via AI Copilot</li>
          <li>Reusability across client cases</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Academic & Research</h3>
        <p><strong>Interdisciplinary Research in Law × Computer Science</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Research datasets of formalized legal norms</li>
          <li>Reproducible research through Validation Gate</li>
          <li>Integration with proof assistants</li>
          <li>Verification foundation for open-set reasoning</li>
          <li>Promotion of interdisciplinary collaboration</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <h2>Case Studies (Coming Soon)</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <p>We are currently implementing with multiple organizations and companies. Details will be published when ready.</p>
      <p><a href="/en/contact" class="button">Contact Us</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

